query:
SELECT blob_sidecar IS NOT NULL as "is_using_blobs"
            FROM eth_txs
            WHERE id = (SELECT MAX(eth_commit_tx_id)
                        FROM l1_batches
                        WHERE eth_commit_tx_id IS NOT NULL
                          AND (SELECT pubdata_type
                               FROM miniblocks
                               WHERE l1_batch_number = l1_batches.number
                               ORDER BY miniblocks.number
                               LIMIT 1) = 'Rollup')
